Package jx.classfile

Class ExceptionHandlerData

java.lang.Object
jx.classfile.ExceptionHandlerData
public class ExceptionHandlerData extends Object
All data about a exception handler, that can be found in a class file. This is a rather passive class. It only reads the data from the class file and stores it.
